-- 03_monthly_metrics.sql
```sql
WITH deduplicated_billing AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount,
    event_type
  FROM billing_events
),
subscriptions_with_metadata AS (
  SELECT
    s.subscription_id,
    s.user_id,
    s.plan_id,
    s.started_at,
    s.ended_at,
    s.status,
    p.tier,
    p.monthly_price,
    c.industry
  FROM subscriptions s
  LEFT JOIN plans p ON s.plan_id = p.plan_id
  LEFT JOIN users u ON s.user_id = u.user_id
  LEFT JOIN companies c ON u.company_id = c.company_id
),
billing_by_month AS (
  SELECT
    b.event_month AS month,
    COALESCE(s.tier, 'Unknown') AS tier,
    COALESCE(s.industry, 'Unknown') AS industry,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.subscription_id) AS active_subscriptions,
    SUM(b.amount) AS total_mrr,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.user_id) AS unique_users
  FROM deduplicated_billing b
  JOIN subscriptions_with_metadata s ON b.subscription_id = s.subscription_id
  WHERE s.ended_at IS NULL OR s.ended_at >= b.event_month
  GROUP BY b.event_month, s.tier, s.industry
)
SELECT
  month,
  tier,
  industry,
  active_subscriptions,
  total_mrr,
  unique_users
FROM billing_by_month
ORDER BY month, tier, industry;
